t to rifkin who gave me a sealed diary. I then returned to katta and gave the diary, and the 2 notes to corporal donfeld. He returned them to me which makes me believe they are quest items. In return for each item he said roughly this...<br><br>a sealed diary (side note: you can't open it) -- Hmm.. I need marias's notes too.<br><br>marias's note(first one not about regan) -- interesting but hardly conclusive.<br><br>marias's other note (about regan) -- there were some leads in here did you follow up on that?<br><br>and then he returns it to me. I guess I need 1 more thing, which i don't know what it is.<br><br>My only conclusion was that I needed to find bregun. Which would take me into your quest. <br><br>I thought I would add this as it answers a few of your questions and makes the story much more confusing. Maybe he's looking for the 2nd or 3rd earring? <br><br>Also, I think it would be wise not to kill the recuso as I believe they play a bigger part of knowing about Seru. That's why i think they were exhiled. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>Now my question is, when you gave the quest items to Donfeld, did you give them seperatly or in the file? He gives a recuso case file (4 slot) if you ask for one, and says to put all evidence found about the recuso in the file and to return it to him, and that not all slots have to be used. Couldn't tell if you had the file or not from your post.<br>Turonyen<br>Level 56 Enchanter<br>Tholuxe Paells <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uabsolutemaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Absolute Master</A> at: 1/9/02 11:53:00 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ugalelan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Galelan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/10/02 4:19:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3752.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Recuso Case Quest</span><hr size=1> Your working on two different quests, for the one in Katta given out by Corpral Donfeld results in this:<br><br>Belt of Galin <br>Lore Magic <br>Slot: Belt <br>8ac 4str 3sta 3agi 5 sv vs magic 5 sv vs cold 5 sv vs fire <br>wt 3.0 all/all<br><br>You need to put the two notes, the staff off of Regan and the diary in the case, combine and turn into Corpral Donfeld.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uhelicon99.showPublicProfile?language=EN>helicon99</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/23/02 1:57:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3752.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Marias in Marus Seru</span><hr size=1> I have completed all parts of this quest but turning in the note to Marias.<br><br>Does anyone know if Marias still spawns in Marus Seru?   if so, is he triggered or does he have a PH?<br><br>Any information would be greatly appreciated. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uhelicon99.showPublicProfile?language=EN>helicon99</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/26/02 1:51:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3752.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Marias Spawn</span><hr size=1> I finished the quest finaly for the this nice bit of resist gear<br><br>&quot;Legioniare Marias&quot; spawns randomly in the zone.  I think he is tied to the Lightcrawler cycle, I killed a Massive Lightcrawler and he spawned very shortly afer.  Not sure though.<br><br>When he spawns he is prone on the ground, I imagine any mobs that will attack Recurso will agro on him and kill him almost instanly.<br><br>I spent about 6hrs in the zone with tracking try to find Marias, so I do not think he spawns every 3 to 5 minutes as indicated by someone else.<br><br>To complete the quest, you need to two notes from Marias and the Diary from Rifkin in shadow haven combined all three in the evicence folder and turn it in for the belt.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=3752.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=3752.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3752.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=3752.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=3752.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3752.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3752.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notific